Renwick USD 267 Bond Issue
April 2 at 9:00 AM Â·

One year ago today, voters approved the USD 267 bond issue to provide:

Improvements for safety and security in all Renwick schools;

Educational enhancements to meet the goals of our Strategic Plan, Kansas CAN, and the state Board of Education;

Additional classroom and support space for enhance and efficient education;

Improvements to upgrade the environment in our schools for learning and teaching; and

Additional space for Physical Education/team sports, and fine arts

What a difference a year makes - as you can see from the recent photos as work progresses at many of our construction sites. We wanted to take this opportunity to say THANK YOU again for the support of our children, our schools, our future. #RenwickProud

